name: BG-Omics
body:
### Welcome to BG-Omics Thermotoga-project repository. This projects aims to compare proteins sequence of one species from an thermotoga to another species in the same genus.The desired result is a data table containing all locus tags of matched protein from the given organisms. ![picture](https://raw.github.com/bgomics/thermotoga/master/resultpage.png) ### Authors and Contributors Project is managed by BGOmics group from Bowling Green State University.
Developers Richard Nyonyi @mutatina, Jacob Newmister @newmisterJ ### Support or Contact contact us at bgomics@gmail.com
